text: Whichello is a rural locality in the Toowoomba Region, Queensland, Australia. In the , Whichello had a population of 31 people. ==Geography== McLean family homestead, Whichelllo, circa 1903 Whichello is on the Darling Downs in southern Queensland. Whichello is similar to many of the localities in the eastern Downs, with the land mostly cleared for agriculture and few facilities or amenities. A two hectare reserve is situated in Whichello School Road. == History == Whichello Provisional School opened circa 1894. On 1 January 1909 it became Whichello State School. It closed circa 1941. ==References== Category:Toowoomba Region Category:Localities in Queensland
